Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.77,0:00:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,補習到今天就結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.45,0:00:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.16,0:00:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒啦 這樣終於...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你還沒有哦
